# FORMAT REFERENCE ONLY. Your team lead gives you a finished ".env" (with the dummy key)
# to drop into this folder next to README.md; you normally do NOT hand-build it.
# If you ever do need to: copy this file to ".env" (drop the ".example") and set the key.
# The scripts read ".env" automatically from any directory; a KLAVIYO_API_KEY environment
# variable, if set, takes priority over the file.
#
# DUMMY Klaviyo account only. Rotate the key before any real / client send.
KLAVIYO_API_KEY=pk_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
KLAVIYO_API_REVISION=2026-04-15
